{"tid":1565823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想幫這被趕出家門的小朋友","createTime":"2019-09-13T09:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T08:53:22.000Z","uid":321315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1eef0da7f50c24d94485a9772b191561f9c16b","tid":1565823,"uid":321315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"[url][url]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhNoF52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhNoF52.png&h=ec433f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網址[/url][/url]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLeon在7月收到大專院校升學通知，曾向家人詢問交學費和申請學貸問題，但未獲回應，由於逾期未交學費失去資格，「變咗人哋讀緊書時候，我自己而家就諗唔到可以做咩，好似空白咗，嘥緊時間。」<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇近期收到Leon求助後，游說院校再給予入學機會，「呢個年輕人佢係喺人生最關鍵一年，究竟佢係咪可以升學落去，呢個時間希望大家能夠伸出援手。」他呼籲家人要互相體諒，不值得因為特首林鄭月娥政權影響關係。<br />\n<br />\nLeon現時僅籌措第一學期學費，亦向院校補交申請，惟入學仍有阻滯，學生登記手續波折重重，未來學費仍要再籌措，令輟學陰霾未散。他覺得今年中秋節畢生難忘，「雖然我知道今個星期五就係（中秋節），但真係諗都唔夠膽諗。」昔日中秋一家歡樂團聚，今晚飯桌是否還有自己一席成疑。他說未來不會放棄家庭關係，希望一家能心平氣和吃一頓飯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到好傷心。如想小小錢比他，是否可以找民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇代捐? 希望有多D兄弟姊妹幫幫他。"},{"pid":"779704ac5512c540b8559dae5720543b75d2e21b","tid":1565823,"uid":242849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8754df8f5c28831a28b489adf5bf1510d28577d3","tid":1565823,"uid":235364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"推 想幫手"},{"pid":"89bf78107dde968f5f8e32b4b6410fd121d9d8b5","tid":1565823,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:01:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c99429540511dace595f96363652e69a80f52fce","tid":1565823,"uid":171240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"21歲仲小朋友"},{"pid":"46f8613af7059513a493bf01c6100212057d0e2a","tid":1565823,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dsoWxkK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdsoWxkK.jpg&h=83ed9bd0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}